          • public static java.lang.Object getSimpleNativePropertyValue(java.lang.Object value, MappingContext mappingContext)

            Convert a value into a type suitable for use in Mongo. Collections and maps are converted recursively. The mapping context is used for the conversion if possible, otherwise toString() is the eventual fallback.

            Parameters:
            value - The value to convert (or null)
            mappingContext - The mapping context.
            Returns:
            The converted value (or null)
